TITLE: Defining Gates in Laravel's AppServiceProvider
DESCRIPTION: Example of defining a gate in the boot method of the AppServiceProvider to determine if a user can update a Post model by comparing user IDs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/laravel/docs/blob/12.x/authorization.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use App\Models\Post;
use App\Models\User;
use Illuminate\Support\Facades\Gate;

/**
 * Bootstrap any application services.
 */
public function boot(): void
{
    Gate::define('update-post', function (User $user, Post $post) {
        return $user->id === $post->user_id;
    });
}
```

