TITLE: Serialize Method for Custom Cast
DESCRIPTION: This shows the definition of a `serialize` method that can be implemented to define how custom cast attributes are serialzed when the model is cast to array or JSON.
SOURCE: https://github.com/laravel/docs/blob/12.x/eloquent-mutators.md#_snippet_33

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
/**
 * Get the serialized representation of the value.
 *
 * @param  array<string, mixed>  $attributes
 */
public function serialize(
    Model $model,
    string $key,
    mixed $value,
    array $attributes,
): string {
    return (string) $value;
}
