TITLE: Counting Related Models
DESCRIPTION: Examples of using withCount to count related models without loading them, including multiple relations and custom constraints.
SOURCE: https://github.com/laravel/docs/blob/12.x/eloquent-relationships.md#2025-04-21_snippet_69

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use App\Models\Post;

$posts = Post::withCount('comments')->get();

foreach ($posts as $post) {
