LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Closure;\nuse App\Models\User;\nuse Illuminate\Support\Facades\Pipeline;\n\n$user = Pipeline::send($user)\n    ->through([\n        function (User $user, Closure $next) {\n            // ...\n\n            return $next($user);\n        },\n        function (User $user, Closure $next) {\n            // ...\n\n            return $next($user);\n        },\n    ])\n    ->then(fn (User $user) => $user);
```

