TITLE: Intersecting Laravel Collection by Association Using Callback (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Compares the collection against another collection or array, returning key/value pairs present in both, using a custom callback for both key and value comparison. Useful for case-insensitive or custom equality checks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/laravel/docs/blob/12.x/collections.md#_snippet_57

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$collection = collect([
    'color' => 'red',
    'Size' => 'M',
    'material' => 'cotton',
]);

